    "Id": "chassisdef_lion_LN-15",
    "Name": "Lion",
    "Details": "The LN-15 abandons the long-range focus of the original entirely, replacing every weapon with a short-range oriented loadout. Three SRM 6 launchers with two tons of ammunition deliver heavy close-range salvos while four Medium Lasers and two Small Lasers fill out the energy suite. Twenty-four heat sinks manage the significantly higher thermal demands of this approach. The LN-15 became the most widely exported variant, reaching the Free Worlds League and Magistracy of Canopus in large numbers.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>",
